---
title: Grilled Garlic Steak & Herby Potatoes plus Shishito Peppers with Lemony Feta Dip & Arugula Salad
description: Whether it’s outside on the grill or inside on a grill pan, this Father’s Day grill-fest is a winner! It stars juicy garlicky grilled bavette steak, a bright balsamic dressed arugula salad with homemade grilled croutons, and tender herby potatoes charred in a foil packet. While you’re cooking, you can serve right-off-the-grill blistered shishito peppers with creamy lemon-feta dip. Father’s Day feast, coming up!
